elem_dict.text: Test.ai provides Equal Employment Opportunities to all employees and applicants for employment and prohibits discrimination and harassment of any type without regard to race, color, religion, age, sex, national origin, disability status, genetics, protected veteran status, sexual orientation, gender identity or expression, or any other characteristic protected by federal, state or local laws.We celebrate diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all employees.Equal Employment Opportunity is the law.
